        "content": "<p>The nucleus of carbon has an excited state where it consists of 3 helium nuclei orbiting each other!   I blogged about it:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://johncarlosbaez.wordpress.com/2021/02/04/the-hoyle-state/\">The Hoyle state</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>My understanding of nuclear physics is pretty weak, so there's lots of fun easy stuff to learn and (therefore) blog about.</p>",
        "id": 225196659,
        "sender_full_name": "John Baez",
        "timestamp": 1612461247
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Weak, hmmm?  So your understanding is mediated by the <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mtext>W</mtext><mo>+</mo></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\text{W}^+</annotation></semantics></math></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"katex-html\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.844561em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">W</span></span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.844561em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.1362300000000003em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mbin mtight\">+</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>, <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mtext>W</mtext><mo>−</mo></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\text{W}^-</annotation></semantics></math></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"katex-html\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.844561em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">W</span></span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.844561em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.1362300000000003em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mbin mtight\">−</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>, and <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>Z</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\text{Z}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"katex-html\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">Z</span></span></span></span></span> bosons?  <span aria-label=\"upside down\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f643\" role=\"img\" title=\"upside down\">:upside_down:</span></p>",
